title: Zoo golden gate — PA timeline, feeding time, goat bleats, keeper departure
story: friendly-zoo
description: Deterministic scheduler beats as behavior-parity proof (AC-2
  scheduler category): PA closing announcements at turns 5/10/15/20, the
  feeding-time fuse at turn 11 with its 8-turn repeats, and hungry-goat
  bleats while in the Petting Zoo. Authored against the TS story
  2026-07-11, then frozen. Revised + extended in Phase C P5 (gate-delta
  audit Entries 2-4, David sign-off 2026-07-12): goats start hungry so
  bleats are pinned from turn 3; feeding is repeatable after each bell;
  keeper departure is witnessed-only (decision 10) with `, once` preserved
  off-stage.

